column2: SELECT   m.SPRC, m.Objid, m.R, m.cz, p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.dered_u,p.dered_g,p.dered_r,p.dered_i,p.dered_z,   s.class,s.subclass,g.specObjID , s.specObjID, s.z as redshift,   g.h_beta_flux, g.oiii_#_flux, g.h_alpha_flux, g.nii_#_flux into SPRC_dr8_with_data from dr1#.PhotoObjAll AS p     JOIN dr1#.SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid     JOIN MyDB.SPRC_dr8 AS m ON m.Objid = p.objid
